title: Complete the Square
text: Group and factor: 4(x**2 + 6x) + 25(y**2 + 8y) $$=$$ $$-336$$. Then complete the square.

title: Divide to Get Standard Form
text: After completing the square: $$\frac{\left(x+3\right)^2}{16}$$ + $$\frac{\left(y+4\right)^2}{4}$$ $$=$$ $$1$$. Identify a $$=$$ $$4$$, $$b$$ $$=$$ $$2$$.
